本文分别用Fit-Hi-C和HiCCUPS确定每个样本中可能存在的染色质相互作用，同时找到样本特异的互作并比较两款软件结果的overlap情况

Fit-Hi-C

  1. 将HiC-Pro的结果转换成Fit-Hi-C需要的输入文件:

python /lustre/user/liclab/pengt/projects/tools/HiC-Pro/bin/utils/hicpro2fithic.py -i 5534N_40000.matrix -b
5534N_40000_abs.bed -s 5534N_40000_iced.matrix.biases -r 40000 -o ./5534N/resolution_40k/ &

  1. 运行Fit-Hi-C:

python /lustre/user/liclab/pengt/projects/tools/fithic/fithic/fithic.py -i fithic.interactionCounts.gz
-f fithic.fragmentMappability.gz -t fithic.biases.gz -r 40000 -L 1 -o ./

  1. 获得统计显著的互作，阈值为FDR<0.01:

python /lustre/user/liclab/pengt/projects/lung/hicpro/5534N/resolution_40k/get_sig.py

HiCCUPS

  1. 从HiC-Pro结果的allvalidpairs文件中取出需要的列：

awk '{$4=$4!="+"; $7=$7!="+"; split($9, frag1, "_"); split($10, frag2, "_"); } $2<=$5{print $1, $4, $2, $3,

'frag1[3], $7, $5, $6, frag2[3], $11, $12 }$5<$2{ print $1, $7, $5, $6, frag2[3], $4, $2, $3, frag1[3], $12, $11}'

/lustre/user/liclab/lirf/Project/hic/bgi/lung-work/lung-hic/6405T/hicpro_result/hic_results/data/5534N/5534N_allValidPairs

> 5534N_allValidPairs &

  1. 取出cis互作的reads pair：

python cis.py

  1. 排序：

sort -k3,3d -k7,7d 5534N_pair > 5534N_sorted_pair &

  1. 获得HiCCUPS需要的.hic文件:

java -Xmx6g -jar /lustre/user/liclab/pengt/projects/tools/juicer/CPU/common/juicer_tools.jar pre -r 40000
5534N_sorted_pair 5534N.hic hg19 &

  1. 运行HiCCUPS:

/lustre/user/liclab/pengt/projects/tools/juicer/CPU/common/juicer_tools hiccups --cpu -m 512 -r 4000 -f .1 -p 1 -i 3
-t 0.02,1.5,1.75,2 -d 80000 &

Compare

  1. 确定每种工具结果中染色质互作的重叠情况:

bedtools pairtopair -slop 20000 -a 5534N -b 5534T_6 > 5534NT

  1. 每个样本两款工具的结果取交集结果统计：
data = read.csv('intersect_result.csv',header = T)
